{"tid":1299573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實監控燈柱同換身分證都好大鑊","createTime":"2019-07-09T05:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:07:16.000Z","uid":74778,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f75ecc525787c864e928fef126ea55361e4ebea3","tid":1299573,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:47:51.000Z","msg":"對政治運動黎講，命名好重要<br />\n當初將反對逃犯修訂條例運動講成反送中，易明易入口<br />\n所以依家要加埋反對社會信用系統的訴求時<br />\n唔好叫啲燈柱做智慧燈柱，要一針見血講出燈柱的危險<br />\n<br />\n亦即係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">監控</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重申7大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n<br />\n6. 承諾不推行社會信用評分制度<br />\n<br />\n7. 拆除所有監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de93fb9b7b72ab7513656dcd414803ea70a05163","tid":1299573,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}